Special assets — major story items with narrative weight.
Each entry: Description | Current Status | Tags

════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
                         CORE MYSTERIES
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

RESONANT STONE
  Description: Soul-jar fragment containing Anchor's fractured identity. Contained in Shiawase Securi-Case 500. Humming.
  Status: Stable. Contained. The fragment that started everything.
  Tags: [Core Mystery] [Fractured Self] [Amplifier]

WAKING STONE
  Description: Dormant kin to soul-jars. Skull-sized river stone etched with frozen lightning patterns. Recovered from Yamatetsu Archive Theta.
  Status: Modified with micro-oscillator bridge. Resonance manually adjustable. Tuned. Stable. Dreaming.
  Tags: [Dormant Meta-Artifact] [Resonant Kin] [Dreaming] [Yamatetsu Archived]

PATIENT BOX
  Description: Ancient wooden box. Older than Waking Stone. Humming with resonant signature—distinct, patient, waiting. Similar to Waking Stone but older.
  Status: Ren touched it. It hummed for her. Marcus: "It's never done that before. It approves."
  Tags: [Ancient Resonance] [The Box Listens] [Waiting] [Ren's Mystery]

STABILIZED ECHO
  Description: A coherent, inert meta-fragment anchored to Anchor via Sovereign Pact at Site Hydra. A dying fragment that chose to become a ward, not a weapon.
  Status: Bound to Anchor. Passive resonant asset. Nature and potential unknown.
  Tags: [Metaphysical Asset] [Sovereign Pact] [Potential Resonance]

════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
                         LIVING ASSETS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

PROJECT ŌKAMI CRYO-TUBE
  Description: Cryo-preserved dwarf. Shiawase liability. Recovered from secondary sea payload. Internal temp: -162°C. Nature: LIVING.
  Status: HOT. Contained. Shiawase is hunting it. Elena's defection made this a high-priority recovery target.
  Tags: [HOT] [Shiawase Liability] [LIVING] [Corporate Target]

SUNSPOT CORE
  Description: Primary ECHO BREACH successor project data. Contains complete research on proto-formsoul incubation, mapping data used in Anchor's soul integration, and evidence that Shiawase can create metaphysical life.
  Status: Decrypted. Actionable. If released, paradigm-shifting scandal.
  Tags: [Immeasurable] [ECHO BREACH Successor] [Blackmail] [Paradigm-Shifting]

ECHO BREACH SUBJECT FILES 01-23
  Description: Complete dossiers on twenty-two other ECHO BREACH fragments. Fragmentation profiles, mortality confirmations, personal histories. Anchor is now the singular authority on the project's human cost.
  Status: Complete. Undisclosed. Twenty-two other souls whose fragments may still exist.
  Tags: [22 Souls] [Human Cost] [Anchor's Burden] [Undisclosed Truth]

K-7 WHISPERING SHARD
  Description: WYRM-SIGN artifact. Paranormal resonance. Originally destined for dragon-connected buyers.
  Status: Secured. Contained. WYRM-SIGN is still watching. Standing: Aggressive (-3).
  Tags: [WYRM-SIGN Artifact] [Dragon-Adjacent] [Watched]

════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
                          INTELLIGENCE
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

MORITA'S NETWORK
  Description: Complete map of Morita's assets: 12 fixers, 8 hitters, 23 informants. Names, locations, leverage points, payment structures.
  Status: Mapped. Actionable. When Morita falls, these people will need to choose.
  Tags: [Intel] [Leverage] [Morita's Web] [Actionable]

THIRD MAN PHOTOGRAPH
  Description: Photograph dated 2079.08.14—the day of Anchor's death. Shows Morita + Dr. Tanaka (Shiawase, presumed dead) + unknown third.
  Status: Unsolved. The third man's face is unknown. His role in Oblivion is unknown.
  Tags: [The Third Man] [Oblivion Aftermath] [Core Mystery] [2079.08.14]

WRIGHT-FISHER PROTOCOL
  Description: Corporate safety procedures for containing "metasapient artifacts." Details Type-4 Null-Field Chambers. Revealed Yamatetsu Archive Theta and Helios Wing locations.
  Status: Actionable. Already used to locate Theta and Helios. May reveal more.
  Tags: [Corporate Protocol] [Archive Locations] [Already Actioned]

SITE HYDRA DATA CORE
  Description: Complete project logs on Moth/J. Voss, Schmidt-Krupp financials, and meta-fragment research. Evidence of Schmidt-Krupp's black-lab operations for Shiawase.
  Status: Decrypted. Actionable. Links Moth Properties to Schmidt-Krupp to Shiawase.
  Tags: [Black Lab Records] [Corporate Trail] [Moth's Web]

