CHRYSALIS PROTOTYPE ENCEPHALON (R6)
  Description: Pre-production encephalon. Never field-issued. Charter R&D priority unknown. Street value: 180,000¥+.
  Status: Uninstalled. Contained. Charter may want it back—or may not know it exists.
  Tags: [Tech] [Prototype] [180k+] [Uninstalled]

SHIAWASE I-DORTON "MORPH" CYBERLIMB SUITE
  Description: Full cyberlimb suite, never issued. Prototype status. Source: Yamatetsu Archive Theta.
  Status: Uninstalled. Contained. Complete set, unused.
  Tags: [Tech] [Prototype] [Full Suite] [Uninstalled]

"EIDOLON" RESONANCE DAMPER (EXPERIMENTAL)
  Description: Experimental resonance-dampening device. One of a kind. Effect on Stabilized Echo, Waking Stone, or Seedling unknown.
  Status: Untested. Potentially dangerous. Potentially useful.
  Tags: [Experimental] [Resonance Tech] [Unknown Effect] [One of a Kind]

