                         EMOTIONAL ASSETS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

FAMILY HOLOGRAPH
  Description: Small framed image of Dr. Keiko Arisugawa with a man and a child. Inscribed: "For Keiko, who remembers why." Recovered from Site 3B. Returned to her.
  Status: In Keiko's possession. She looks at it sometimes. She remembers why.
  Tags: [Arisugawa's Catalyst] [Debt Owed] [Symbol of Protection] [Moral Center]

REN'S DRAWING COLLECTION
  Description: Dozens of drawings. Includes "Anchor Far," "Anchor Watching," "Anchor Wanting In." A child's perception of a man learning to come close.
  Status: Pinned on the Nexus wall. Priceless. Also: proof that the box listens to her.
  Tags: [Ren's Gaze] [Artifacts of Trust] [Priceless] [The Box Approves]

HANA'S MEDICAL RECORDS
  Description: Multiple sclerosis diagnosis. Progressive. Current status, treatment history, projected needs.
  Status: Active. Priority care. No timer, but the clock ticks.
  Tags: [Medical Intel] [Vulnerability] [Priority Care] [Morita's Heart]

MORITA'S PERSONAL FILES
  Description: Photographs of Ren's life. Hana's video message to Morita. Complete portrait of the family he couldn't keep.
  Status: Anchor holds them. If Morita discovers this, the reckoning will be absolute.
  Tags: [Emotional Intel] [Morita's Heart] [Complicated Leverage] [Reckoning Fuel]

